org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.tree.as

Interface IInitializableDefinitionNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IDefinitionNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseVariableNode, ChainedVariableNode, ConfigConstNode, ConfigNamespaceNode, NamespaceNode, ParameterNode, VariableNode

    public interface IInitializableDefinitionNode
extends IDefinitionNode
    AST node for a definition that can have a initializer. Such as variable definition (var x = 100), namespace definition ( namespace ns = "foo").

    This interface provides a mutable view of the implementing AST node, so it is hidden in the internal package.
